## H. Integration Points

### H.1 With Version Control

```bash
# Create feature branch and worktree
python -m orchestrator --project "Implement OAuth2" \
                       --criteria "Tests pass" \
                       # Automatically commits to feature branch
```

### H.2 With CI/CD

```yaml
# GitHub Actions example
- name: Orchestrate implementation
  run: |
    python -m orchestrator --project "$PROJECT_DESC" \
                           --criteria "$CRITERIA" \
                           --budget 5.0
    pytest
```

### H.3 With External LLMs

```python
from orchestrator import Orchestrator, Model

orch = Orchestrator()
# Automatically uses available providers:
# OpenAI (GPT-4o, GPT-4o-mini)
# Google (Gemini 2.5 Pro, Flash)
# Anthropic (Claude Opus, Sonnet, Haiku)
# DeepSeek (DeepSeek Chat, Reasoner)
# Kimi (Kimi K2.5)
```

