## I. Configuration & Environment

### I.1 API Keys

Set in `.env`:
```
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
GOOGLE_GENAI_API_KEY=...
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=...
KIMI_API_KEY=...
```

### I.2 Settings

Via `.claude/settings.local.json`:
```json
{
  "hooks": {
    "startup": ["validate-env"]
  },
  "cache": {
    "type": "disk",
    "ttl_seconds": 86400
  }
}
```

